metadata.name: PunkMoonbird #1
metadata.description: Punk Moonbirds is a collection of 10,000 NFTs that feature unique pool of rarity-powered traits of the original CryptoPunks created special for the Moonbirds. The #numbers of Punk Moonbirds and their attributes are based on their equivalent likeness of CryptoPunks! This project pays homage to the original Moonbirds project and CryptoPunks. Not affiliated with Larva Labs and any other projects.
